{
  "stem": "23090.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they began to then take the-- the-- the younger people were now being taken out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were asked to come and work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would tell them that they would just leave for a week or two, because they needed them to build certain roads and so on, and that they would a-- reward them.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you see more young people being ta-- leaving the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "During the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "During the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1943, '43, '44, beginning of '44.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There's sta-- there has now become a little unrest, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There's just-- You are now living un-- under terrible, terrible conditions.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Since the Germans themselves are now, as I see, and I'm able now to see why these things happen, not getting enough food for their--",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they are now denying the little ra-- the rations that we used to get were now cut down to virtually a minimum ration.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so everything that we had when the ghetto started and as it was progressing for a while was now being taken away.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And now you're starting to see the-- the-- the results of hunger and sickness and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And while there was hope that we're going to be liberated somehow by the Russians-- there was no such thing as mentioning about Americans, since Russia was the next place to us-- it is now becoming a-- a-- a-- rumor that we're going some other places.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And now the-- again, the conversation in family and in circles and wherever you go as a young boy.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whether you go to work, you hear the same thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There's no more playing out in the streets.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There is nothing to play with.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's-- you're hungry.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
